<template><h1 id="toast-提示框" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#toast-提示框" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Toast 提示框</h1>
<h2 id="概述" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#概述" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 概述</h2>
<p>一种轻量级反馈/提示，一般用于消息通知、加载提示、操作结果提示等场景。</p>
<h2 id="示例" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#示例" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 示例</h2>
<div class="language-html ext-html line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-html"><code>基础用法 <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>a-toast</span> <span class="token attr-name">toastData</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>{{ toastData }}<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>a-toast</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token function">Page</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>
